nodup_to_list:
@[simp]
theorem nodup_to_list [fin_enum α] : List.Nodup (to_list α) := by
  simp [to_list] <;> apply List.Nodup.map <;> [apply Equiv.injective, apply List.nodup_finRange]
#align nodup_to_list nodup_to_list

@[simp]
theorem mem_to_list [fin_enum α] (x : α) : x ∈ to_list α := by simp [to_list] <;> exists equiv α x <;> simp
#align mem_to_list mem_to_list
mem_pi:
theorem mem_pi {β : α → Type max u v} [fin_enum α] [∀ a, fin_enum (β a)] (xs : list α) (f : ∀ a, a ∈ xs → β a) :
    f ∈ pi xs fun x => to_list (β x) :=
  by
  induction xs <;> simp [pi, -List.map_eq_map, monad_norm, functor_norm]
  · ext (a⟨⟩)
  · exists pi.cons xs_hd xs_tl (f _ (list.mem_cons_self _ _))
    constructor
    exact ⟨_, rfl⟩
    exists pi.tail f
    constructor
    · apply xs_ih
    · ext (x h)
      simp [pi.cons]
      split_ifs
      subst x
      rfl
      rfl
#align mem_pi mem_pi
mem_enum:
theorem pi.mem_enum {β : α → Type max u v} [fin_enum α] [∀ a, fin_enum (β a)] (f : ∀ a, β a) : f ∈ pi.enum β := by
  simp [pi.enum] <;> refine' ⟨fun a h => f a, mem_pi _ _, rfl⟩
#align pi.mem_enum pi.mem_enum
